    description: 'East Winds is a boutique all-inclusive on Saint Lucia\'s calmer northwest coast, set on a quiet cove near Gros Islet. The property keeps its scale small — just a few dozen cottages tucked into tropical gardens — and leans on personalized service rather than mega-resort amenities. Food and drink quality consistently rank above the island average for the category.',
