    description: 'Trobbu Boutique Collection is a small jungle-set all-inclusive in Tulum, designed around oversized rooms and a quieter, slower pace than the bigger Riviera Maya resorts. It is pet-friendly — still uncommon in the all-inclusive category — and welcomes families. The property leans boutique-and-residential rather than full-amenity, with a compact list of facilities and a focus on the surrounding jungle setting.',
