    activities: 'Days revolve around guided wildlife outings — Corcovado hikes for tapir, monkeys, and scarlet macaws; Cano Island snorkel and dive trips; and night walks for frogs and insects. The all-inclusive covers meals and basic on-site activities like kayaking the estuary, while signature excursions are typically booked as add-ons. Whale-watching from July to October and again December through March is a notable draw.',
