    whatYouNeedToKnow: 'From Belize City (BZE) take a short Tropic Air or Maya Island Air flight to San Pedro (SPR), followed by a roughly 20-minute boat or golf-cart transfer up the coast. The all-inclusive covers meals, beach access, bicycles, snorkelling gear, and most non-motorized watersports; alcohol, diving, fishing, and spa treatments are charged separately. Guests are 16 and up. Belize is in the Atlantic hurricane belt; September and October are the highest-risk months.',
    bestTimeToVisit: 'Late November through April is dry season with the best reef visibility and most reliable weather. Whale shark season off the southern reef runs roughly March through June. The wet and hurricane season runs June through November with peak storm risk in September and October.',
